These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-7-1::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: september, may, february, june, july, december, march
1. the person who's birthday is in march is in the middle##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
3. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's birthday is in march##7
4. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in september##5
5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
6. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |   2    |    3    |   4    |    5    |     6     |  7   |
| Birthday   | july | december | february | march | september | may | june |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-7-2::.
House: art-deco, modern, palace, wooden, farmhouse, tower, futuristic
 1. the palace house is somewhere to the left of the wooden house##5
 2. the palace house is somewhere between the futuristic house and the modern house##7
 3. the modern house is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3
 4. the art-deco house is somewhere to the right of the wooden house##5
 5. the wooden house is somewhere between the art-deco house and the farmhouse house##7
 6. the palace house is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
 7. the tower house is on the left or right of the wooden house##3
 8. the tower house is somewhere to the left of the wooden house##5
 9. the farmhouse house is somewhere to the left of the modern house##5
10. the modern house is on the left or right of the farmhouse house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2       |    3     |    4    |      5      |     6      |   7    |
| House   | futuristic | palace | farmhouse | modern | tower | wooden | art-deco |

