1. the french is somewhere between the malaysian and the australian##7
2. the australian is somewhere between the brazilian and the french##7
3. the turkish is somewhere to the left of the australian##5
4. the turkish is somewhere between the colombian and the malaysian##7
5. the french is somewhere to the right of the australian##5
6. the brazilian is somewhere between the french and the turkish##7
7. the turkish is somewhere to the left of the australian##5
8. the dutch is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1  |   2   |   3    |   4   |     5      |  6  |     7      |
| Nationality   | colombian | turkish | brazilian | australian | french | malaysian | dutch |

