3. the person who growsazalea is in an odd position##4
4. the person who growszinnia is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdahlia##5
5. the person who growsazalea is between the person who growsdaffodil and the person who growsdahlia##2
6. the person who growstulip is somewhere to the right of the person who growsdaffodil##5
7. the person who growstulip is somewhere to the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##5
