.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-7-8::.
7 different games are played: canasta, chess, snooker, billiard, go, bridge, scrabble
 1. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing chess##1
 2. the person playing billiard is in an odd position##4
 3. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the left of the person playing go##5
 4. the person playing snooker is somewhere between the person playing canasta and the person playing go##7
 5. the person playing snooker is somewhere between the person playing scrabble and the person playing canasta##7
 6. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the left of the person playing chess##5
 7. the person playing bridge is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 9. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the left of the person playing scrabble##5
10. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
11. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |       1        |    2     |    3     |   4    |       5        |      6      |     7     |
| Game   | bridge | canasta | snooker | scrabble | billiard | chess | go |

