 4. the vegafina-smoker is on the left or right of the blend-smoker##3
 5. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 6. the game-smoker is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
 7. the blend-smoker is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
 8. the pall-mall-smoker is somewhere to the left of the davidoff-smoker##5
 9. the tiparillo-smoker is somewhere to the left of the davidoff-smoker##5
10. the pall-mall-smoker is somewhere to the right of the tiparillo-smoker##5

