4. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
5. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere between the person driving the helicopter and the person driving the car##7
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
7. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
