.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-7-11::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: comedy, documentary, time-travel, family, scientific, thriller, western
1. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching scientific movies##5
2. the person watching western movies is somewhere between the person watching documentary movies and the person watching comedy movies##7
3. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere between the person watching western movies and the person watching thriller movies##7
4. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching comedy movies##5
5. the person watching thriller movies is between the person watching documentary movies and the person watching family movies##2
6. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
7. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person watching documentary movies is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |   3    |  4   |   5   |  6   |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | family | thriller | documentary | scientific | western | comedy |

