 4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
 5. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere between the person who's hobby is chess and the person who's hobby is skydiving##7
 6. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 7. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
10. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##5

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1      |  2  |  3   |   4    |   5   |  6   |  7   |
| Hobby   | cooking | baking | chess | drawing | video-games | gardening | skydiving |

