3. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the right of the person playing canasta##5
4. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
5. the person playing domino is somewhere between the person playing whist and the person playing monopoly##7
6. the person playing monopoly is the person playing monopoly##1
7. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing domino##1
8. the person playing domino is somewhere to the left of the person playing billiard##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3   |   4    |    5     |     6     |     7     |
| Game   | whist | domino | billiard | canasta | scrabble | go | monopoly |

 